HEADWORD: Double-acting
<hw>Dou"ble-act`ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Acting or
operating in two directions or with both motions; producing a twofold
result; <as>as, a <ex>double-acting</ex> engine or pump</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

